{"expireTime":9007200905229170000,"key":"transformer-remark-markdown-html-ast-50b8540cf5ebb61d0c1a2cdd688de534-gatsby-remark-autolink-headersgatsby-remark-prismjsgatsby-remark-copy-linked-filesgatsby-remark-unwrap-imagesgatsby-remark-imagesgatsby-remark-smartypants-","val":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"/blog/product-design-principles-hero.jpg","alt":"product design principles graphic"},"children":[],"position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":1,"offset":1},"end":{"line":2,"column":79,"offset":79}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"As we’ve grown over the last few months, the Sourcegraph design and product teams have found ourselves having more discussions around product and design decisions. This is a common challenge for design teams everywhere: there are often many valid ways to solve a problem, each with its own set of tradeoffs and assumptions. A small team can rely on intuition, experience, and shared trust to make decisions in these moments. ","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1,"offset":81},"end":{"line":4,"column":426,"offset":506}}},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"But gut instinct doesn’t scale.","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":428,"offset":508},"end":{"line":4,"column":459,"offset":539}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":426,"offset":506},"end":{"line":4,"column":461,"offset":541}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1,"offset":81},"end":{"line":4,"column":461,"offset":541}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The design and product teams were at an inflection point. That’s why we decided it was time to come together to define our product design principles. I’m going to go into how we did this and what principles we settled on, but first I’ll cover some basics:","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1,"offset":543},"end":{"line":6,"column":256,"offset":798}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1,"offset":543},"end":{"line":6,"column":256,"offset":798}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"What-are-product-design-principles","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#What-are-product-design-principles","aria-label":"What are product design principles permalink","class":"anchor before"},"children":[{"type":"raw","value":"<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 18 95 120\" height=\"18\" width=\"18\"><path d=\"M53.69,78.7H37.94l-5.85,25H21.74l5.85-25H15.89L18,69.1H29.84l4.65-19.65H23.39l2.1-9.6H36.74l5.7-23.7H52.79l-5.7,23.7H62.84l5.7-23.7H78.89l-5.7,23.7H84.74l-2.4,9.6H70.94L66.29,69.1H77.24l-2.4,9.6H64l-5.85,25H47.84Zm-13.5-9.6H55.94l4.65-19.65H44.84Z\"/></svg>"}]},{"type":"text","value":"What are product design principles?","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":4,"offset":803},"end":{"line":8,"column":39,"offset":838}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1,"offset":800},"end":{"line":8,"column":39,"offset":838}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Product design principles are a set of statements co-created by the team to express a shared vision and values for the product.","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1,"offset":840},"end":{"line":10,"column":128,"offset":967}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1,"offset":840},"end":{"line":10,"column":128,"offset":967}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A strong set of product design principles gives the team a way to make ","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1,"offset":969},"end":{"line":12,"column":72,"offset":1040}}},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"consistent decisions","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":74,"offset":1042},"end":{"line":12,"column":94,"offset":1062}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":72,"offset":1040},"end":{"line":12,"column":96,"offset":1064}}},{"type":"text","value":" based on a shared idea of what we’re trying to achieve. They ","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":96,"offset":1064},"end":{"line":12,"column":158,"offset":1126}}},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"introduce constraints","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":160,"offset":1128},"end":{"line":12,"column":181,"offset":1149}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":158,"offset":1126},"end":{"line":12,"column":183,"offset":1151}}},{"type":"text","value":" that help reduce ambiguity, particularly when there’s more than one possible solution to a given problem. They also give us a way to ","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":183,"offset":1151},"end":{"line":12,"column":317,"offset":1285}}},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"capture our commitment to inclusion","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":319,"offset":1287},"end":{"line":12,"column":354,"offset":1322}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":317,"offset":1285},"end":{"line":12,"column":356,"offset":1324}}},{"type":"text","value":" at every step of the design process.","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":356,"offset":1324},"end":{"line":12,"column":393,"offset":1361}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1,"offset":969},"end":{"line":12,"column":393,"offset":1361}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"Who-uses-product-design-principles","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#Who-uses-product-design-principles","aria-label":"Who uses product design principles permalink","class":"anchor before"},"children":[{"type":"raw","value":"<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 18 95 120\" height=\"18\" width=\"18\"><path d=\"M53.69,78.7H37.94l-5.85,25H21.74l5.85-25H15.89L18,69.1H29.84l4.65-19.65H23.39l2.1-9.6H36.74l5.7-23.7H52.79l-5.7,23.7H62.84l5.7-23.7H78.89l-5.7,23.7H84.74l-2.4,9.6H70.94L66.29,69.1H77.24l-2.4,9.6H64l-5.85,25H47.84Zm-13.5-9.6H55.94l4.65-19.65H44.84Z\"/></svg>"}]},{"type":"text","value":"Who uses product design principles?","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":4,"offset":1366},"end":{"line":14,"column":39,"offset":1401}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1,"offset":1363},"end":{"line":14,"column":39,"offset":1401}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"While they might be called product design principles, they’re for everyone in the organization.","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1,"offset":1403},"end":{"line":16,"column":96,"offset":1498}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1,"offset":1403},"end":{"line":16,"column":96,"offset":1498}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Designers use design principles to guide their explorations and outcomes. Product managers use design principles to shape priorities and features. Developers use design principles as a lens to collaborate on design, from discovery to delivery.","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1,"offset":1500},"end":{"line":18,"column":244,"offset":1743}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1,"offset":1500},"end":{"line":18,"column":244,"offset":1743}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{"id":"Sidebar-Whats-the-difference-between-design-principles-and-design-patterns","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#Sidebar-Whats-the-difference-between-design-principles-and-design-patterns","aria-label":"Sidebar Whats the difference between design principles and design patterns permalink","class":"anchor before"},"children":[{"type":"raw","value":"<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 18 95 120\" height=\"18\" width=\"18\"><path d=\"M53.69,78.7H37.94l-5.85,25H21.74l5.85-25H15.89L18,69.1H29.84l4.65-19.65H23.39l2.1-9.6H36.74l5.7-23.7H52.79l-5.7,23.7H62.84l5.7-23.7H78.89l-5.7,23.7H84.74l-2.4,9.6H70.94L66.29,69.1H77.24l-2.4,9.6H64l-5.85,25H47.84Zm-13.5-9.6H55.94l4.65-19.65H44.84Z\"/></svg>"}]},{"type":"text","value":"Sidebar: What’s the difference between design principles and design patterns?","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":5,"offset":1749},"end":{"line":20,"column":82,"offset":1826}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1,"offset":1745},"end":{"line":20,"column":82,"offset":1826}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Design principles and design patterns are often conflated. Where design principles are simple, broadly applicable, and capture our shared vision and values, design patterns are the tangible and repeatable expression of our principles in combination with heuristics of good design and usability.","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1,"offset":1828},"end":{"line":22,"column":295,"offset":2122}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1,"offset":1828},"end":{"line":22,"column":295,"offset":2122}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Design principles don’t change often, as they reflect a core truth of who we are. Design patterns change over time to meet new needs, technology, and trends.","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1,"offset":2124},"end":{"line":24,"column":158,"offset":2281}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1,"offset":2124},"end":{"line":24,"column":158,"offset":2281}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"How-we-defined-our-product-design-principles","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#How-we-defined-our-product-design-principles","aria-label":"How we defined our product design principles permalink","class":"anchor before"},"children":[{"type":"raw","value":"<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 18 95 120\" height=\"18\" width=\"18\"><path d=\"M53.69,78.7H37.94l-5.85,25H21.74l5.85-25H15.89L18,69.1H29.84l4.65-19.65H23.39l2.1-9.6H36.74l5.7-23.7H52.79l-5.7,23.7H62.84l5.7-23.7H78.89l-5.7,23.7H84.74l-2.4,9.6H70.94L66.29,69.1H77.24l-2.4,9.6H64l-5.85,25H47.84Zm-13.5-9.6H55.94l4.65-19.65H44.84Z\"/></svg>"}]},{"type":"text","value":"How we defined our product design principles","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":4,"offset":2286},"end":{"line":26,"column":48,"offset":2330}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1,"offset":2283},"end":{"line":26,"column":48,"offset":2330}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"At Sourcegraph, we’re fully remote and globally distributed. Our product and design teams span 13 time zones.\nThat’s why we prioritize asynchronous collaboration together with thoughtful moments of real-time collaboration.","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1,"offset":2332},"end":{"line":29,"column":113,"offset":2554}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1,"offset":2332},"end":{"line":29,"column":113,"offset":2554}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"We wanted to involve product designers, product managers, and engineers throughout the process to co-create our design principles. To make sure we could create the best collaborative environment, we planned a process that would start asynchronously before bringing us together for a real-time workshop when we needed an immediate feedback loop.","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1,"offset":2556},"end":{"line":31,"column":345,"offset":2900}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1,"offset":2556},"end":{"line":31,"column":345,"offset":2900}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"The-process","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#The-process","aria-label":"The process permalink","class":"anchor before"},"children":[{"type":"raw","value":"<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 18 95 120\" height=\"18\" width=\"18\"><path d=\"M53.69,78.7H37.94l-5.85,25H21.74l5.85-25H15.89L18,69.1H29.84l4.65-19.65H23.39l2.1-9.6H36.74l5.7-23.7H52.79l-5.7,23.7H62.84l5.7-23.7H78.89l-5.7,23.7H84.74l-2.4,9.6H70.94L66.29,69.1H77.24l-2.4,9.6H64l-5.85,25H47.84Zm-13.5-9.6H55.94l4.65-19.65H44.84Z\"/></svg>"}]},{"type":"text","value":"The process","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":4,"offset":2905},"end":{"line":33,"column":15,"offset":2916}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1,"offset":2902},"end":{"line":33,"column":15,"offset":2916}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{"id":"1-Aligning-on-our-goals-and-conceptual-understanding-of-principles","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#1-Aligning-on-our-goals-and-conceptual-understanding-of-principles","aria-label":"1 Aligning on our goals and conceptual understanding of principles permalink","class":"anchor before"},"children":[{"type":"raw","value":"<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 18 95 120\" height=\"18\" width=\"18\"><path d=\"M53.69,78.7H37.94l-5.85,25H21.74l5.85-25H15.89L18,69.1H29.84l4.65-19.65H23.39l2.1-9.6H36.74l5.7-23.7H52.79l-5.7,23.7H62.84l5.7-23.7H78.89l-5.7,23.7H84.74l-2.4,9.6H70.94L66.29,69.1H77.24l-2.4,9.6H64l-5.85,25H47.84Zm-13.5-9.6H55.94l4.65-19.65H44.84Z\"/></svg>"}]},{"type":"text","value":"1. Aligning on our goals and conceptual understanding of principles","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":5,"offset":2922},"end":{"line":35,"column":72,"offset":2989}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1,"offset":2918},"end":{"line":35,"column":72,"offset":2989}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"We created a ","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1,"offset":2991},"end":{"line":37,"column":14,"offset":3004}}},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/10Ko8z1ozVaUStuPG2-cM_EJUVJvcgabv8qZYNAJXn24/edit#"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"shared working doc","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":15,"offset":3005},"end":{"line":37,"column":33,"offset":3023}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":14,"offset":3004},"end":{"line":37,"column":121,"offset":3111}}},{"type":"text","value":" where we broke down our understanding of design principles, how they’re used, and how we would use them. This gave us a target and alignment around a shared conceptual understanding of principles and what we were trying to achieve.","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":121,"offset":3111},"end":{"line":37,"column":353,"offset":3343}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1,"offset":2991},"end":{"line":37,"column":353,"offset":3343}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{"id":"2-Digging-in-individually-to-reflect-on-principles-in-action-ahead-of-the-workshop","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#2-Digging-in-individually-to-reflect-on-principles-in-action-ahead-of-the-workshop","aria-label":"2 Digging in individually to reflect on principles in action ahead of the workshop permalink","class":"anchor before"},"children":[{"type":"raw","value":"<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 18 95 120\" height=\"18\" width=\"18\"><path d=\"M53.69,78.7H37.94l-5.85,25H21.74l5.85-25H15.89L18,69.1H29.84l4.65-19.65H23.39l2.1-9.6H36.74l5.7-23.7H52.79l-5.7,23.7H62.84l5.7-23.7H78.89l-5.7,23.7H84.74l-2.4,9.6H70.94L66.29,69.1H77.24l-2.4,9.6H64l-5.85,25H47.84Zm-13.5-9.6H55.94l4.65-19.65H44.84Z\"/></svg>"}]},{"type":"text","value":"2. Digging in individually to reflect on principles in action ahead of the workshop","position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":5,"offset":3349},"end":{"line":39,"column":88,"offset":3432}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":1,"offset":3345},"end":{"line":39,"column":88,"offset":3432}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ahead of the workshop, we did some homework. Each member of the team went off to explore and reflect on how other organizations defined their principles, and how those principles were reflected in their products.","position":{"start":{"line":41,"column":1,"offset":3434},"end":{"line":41,"column":213,"offset":3646}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":41,"column":1,"offset":3434},"end":{"line":41,"column":213,"offset":3646}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{"id":"3-Workshop","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#3-Workshop","aria-label":"3 Workshop permalink","class":"anchor before"},"children":[{"type":"raw","value":"<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 18 95 120\" height=\"18\" width=\"18\"><path d=\"M53.69,78.7H37.94l-5.85,25H21.74l5.85-25H15.89L18,69.1H29.84l4.65-19.65H23.39l2.1-9.6H36.74l5.7-23.7H52.79l-5.7,23.7H62.84l5.7-23.7H78.89l-5.7,23.7H84.74l-2.4,9.6H70.94L66.29,69.1H77.24l-2.4,9.6H64l-5.85,25H47.84Zm-13.5-9.6H55.94l4.65-19.65H44.84Z\"/></svg>"}]},{"type":"text","value":"3. Workshop","position":{"start":{"line":43,"column":5,"offset":3652},"end":{"line":43,"column":16,"offset":3663}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":43,"column":1,"offset":3648},"end":{"line":43,"column":16,"offset":3663}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"To bring us together and create a quick feedback loop, we facilitated a workshop with designers, product managers, and engineers. As a warm-up activity, everyone took turns sharing reflections from their homework to get everyone in the right frame of mind.","position":{"start":{"line":45,"column":1,"offset":3665},"end":{"line":45,"column":257,"offset":3921}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":45,"column":1,"offset":3665},"end":{"line":45,"column":257,"offset":3921}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Then, we spent some time individually generating ideas, before collectively finding themes emerging across the team. Everyone joined in to group and label these themes, which we then used as the basis for a guided discussion around each theme.","position":{"start":{"line":47,"column":1,"offset":3923},"end":{"line":47,"column":244,"offset":4166}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":47,"column":1,"offset":3923},"end":{"line":47,"column":244,"offset":4166}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Finally, we shifted back to an asynchronous workflow to cast anonymous votes for the themes that resonated most strongly with each of us as individuals.","position":{"start":{"line":49,"column":1,"offset":4168},"end":{"line":49,"column":153,"offset":4320}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":49,"column":1,"offset":4168},"end":{"line":49,"column":153,"offset":4320}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"/blog/evolving-workshop-themes.png","alt":"Uncovering themes among ideas"},"children":[],"position":{"start":{"line":51,"column":1,"offset":4322},"end":{"line":51,"column":69,"offset":4390}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{"id":"4-Continuation-and-refinement","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#4-Continuation-and-refinement","aria-label":"4 Continuation and refinement permalink","class":"anchor before"},"children":[{"type":"raw","value":"<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 18 95 120\" height=\"18\" width=\"18\"><path d=\"M53.69,78.7H37.94l-5.85,25H21.74l5.85-25H15.89L18,69.1H29.84l4.65-19.65H23.39l2.1-9.6H36.74l5.7-23.7H52.79l-5.7,23.7H62.84l5.7-23.7H78.89l-5.7,23.7H84.74l-2.4,9.6H70.94L66.29,69.1H77.24l-2.4,9.6H64l-5.85,25H47.84Zm-13.5-9.6H55.94l4.65-19.65H44.84Z\"/></svg>"}]},{"type":"text","value":"4. Continuation and refinement","position":{"start":{"line":53,"column":5,"offset":4396},"end":{"line":53,"column":35,"offset":4426}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":53,"column":1,"offset":4392},"end":{"line":53,"column":35,"offset":4426}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"One of the trickiest parts of a collective activity is bridging the gap between collective work and cohesive outcomes.","position":{"start":{"line":55,"column":1,"offset":4428},"end":{"line":55,"column":119,"offset":4546}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":55,"column":1,"offset":4428},"end":{"line":55,"column":119,"offset":4546}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"To keep us moving forward, one member of our team took the outcomes of the workshop—the themes, the notes from our discussion, and the voting—and wrote a first draft of our potential product design principles. This artifact became the basis for further continuation and refinement.","position":{"start":{"line":57,"column":1,"offset":4548},"end":{"line":57,"column":282,"offset":4829}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":57,"column":1,"offset":4548},"end":{"line":57,"column":282,"offset":4829}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{"id":"5-Sharing-and-collecting-feedback-from-the-whole-organization","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#5-Sharing-and-collecting-feedback-from-the-whole-organization","aria-label":"5 Sharing and collecting feedback from the whole organization permalink","class":"anchor before"},"children":[{"type":"raw","value":"<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 18 95 120\" height=\"18\" width=\"18\"><path d=\"M53.69,78.7H37.94l-5.85,25H21.74l5.85-25H15.89L18,69.1H29.84l4.65-19.65H23.39l2.1-9.6H36.74l5.7-23.7H52.79l-5.7,23.7H62.84l5.7-23.7H78.89l-5.7,23.7H84.74l-2.4,9.6H70.94L66.29,69.1H77.24l-2.4,9.6H64l-5.85,25H47.84Zm-13.5-9.6H55.94l4.65-19.65H44.84Z\"/></svg>"}]},{"type":"text","value":"5. Sharing and collecting feedback from the whole organization","position":{"start":{"line":59,"column":5,"offset":4835},"end":{"line":59,"column":67,"offset":4897}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":59,"column":1,"offset":4831},"end":{"line":59,"column":67,"offset":4897}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Once we all felt strongly that our product design principles captured our team’s vision and values, we shared our proposed principles as an ","position":{"start":{"line":61,"column":1,"offset":4899},"end":{"line":61,"column":141,"offset":5039}}},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1zRbtZR68ZITYypSAJJ63Ir_fFPxJfTtidJmsrxUXW7o/edit#"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"RFC","position":{"start":{"line":61,"column":142,"offset":5040},"end":{"line":61,"column":145,"offset":5043}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":61,"column":141,"offset":5039},"end":{"line":61,"column":233,"offset":5131}}},{"type":"text","value":" with everyone at Sourcegraph, which you can now read too.","position":{"start":{"line":61,"column":233,"offset":5131},"end":{"line":61,"column":291,"offset":5189}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":61,"column":1,"offset":4899},"end":{"line":61,"column":291,"offset":5189}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"Sourcegraphs-product-design-principles","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#Sourcegraphs-product-design-principles","aria-label":"Sourcegraphs product design principles permalink","class":"anchor before"},"children":[{"type":"raw","value":"<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 18 95 120\" height=\"18\" width=\"18\"><path d=\"M53.69,78.7H37.94l-5.85,25H21.74l5.85-25H15.89L18,69.1H29.84l4.65-19.65H23.39l2.1-9.6H36.74l5.7-23.7H52.79l-5.7,23.7H62.84l5.7-23.7H78.89l-5.7,23.7H84.74l-2.4,9.6H70.94L66.29,69.1H77.24l-2.4,9.6H64l-5.85,25H47.84Zm-13.5-9.6H55.94l4.65-19.65H44.84Z\"/></svg>"}]},{"type":"text","value":"Sourcegraph’s product design principles","position":{"start":{"line":63,"column":4,"offset":5194},"end":{"line":63,"column":43,"offset":5233}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":63,"column":1,"offset":5191},"end":{"line":63,"column":43,"offset":5233}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A personal tool within a larger workflow","position":{"start":{"line":65,"column":5,"offset":5239},"end":{"line":65,"column":45,"offset":5279}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":65,"column":3,"offset":5237},"end":{"line":65,"column":47,"offset":5281}}},{"type":"raw","value":"<br />","position":{"start":{"line":65,"column":47,"offset":5281},"end":{"line":65,"column":53,"offset":5287}}},{"type":"text","value":"\nSourcegraph is a powerful yet personal tool that exists within a larger workflow. Design for familiar patterns with thoughtful defaults, while embracing personalization and adaptability.","position":{"start":{"line":65,"column":53,"offset":5287},"end":{"line":66,"column":189,"offset":5476}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":65,"column":1,"offset":5235},"end":{"line":67,"column":1,"offset":5477}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Made for everyone","position":{"start":{"line":68,"column":5,"offset":5482},"end":{"line":68,"column":22,"offset":5499}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":68,"column":3,"offset":5480},"end":{"line":68,"column":24,"offset":5501}}},{"type":"raw","value":"<br />","position":{"start":{"line":68,"column":24,"offset":5501},"end":{"line":68,"column":30,"offset":5507}}},{"type":"text","value":"\nOur purpose is to make it so ","position":{"start":{"line":68,"column":30,"offset":5507},"end":{"line":69,"column":32,"offset":5539}}},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://handbook.sourcegraph.com/company/strategy#purpose"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"everyone can code","position":{"start":{"line":69,"column":33,"offset":5540},"end":{"line":69,"column":50,"offset":5557}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":69,"column":32,"offset":5539},"end":{"line":69,"column":110,"offset":5617}}},{"type":"text","value":". This demands we make Sourcegraph accessible and useful for all developers through universal, inclusive design.","position":{"start":{"line":69,"column":110,"offset":5617},"end":{"line":69,"column":222,"offset":5729}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":68,"column":1,"offset":5478},"end":{"line":70,"column":1,"offset":5730}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Gracefully manage complexity","position